              <note>An anonymous Sh&#x12B;&#x2BB;i commentary on S&#x16B;rah 67 (al-Mulk )</note>
              <note>The commentary is similar to the preceding work on S&#x16B;rah 36, but a number of
                earlier authorities are mentioned by name. Numerous anecdotes of the prophets and
                early mystics are introduced, especially at the beginning</note>
